<br>
Anyway, the main jist of what I want to know is how does a monk make money in EQ?  I'm level 38, and I have less than 100pp in the bank.  I need to upgrade my equipment (or my weapons, at least), but I can't afford anything better (I'm using 2 CoT's right now).  My guild isn't full of 55+ monks (or 55+ anything, for that matter), so I can't really enlist their help.  The only thing I can think of to do is buy what I need.  And there lies the root of my problem:  no money.<br>
<br>
